{panel:borderStyle=solid|borderColor=#080|bgColor=#080}
{color:#fff}This screams "resolved"{color}
{panel}

On the other hand, switching to list view in issue navigator shows light, washed out colors, in a way defeating the whole point of having color-based identification and forcing the user to have to read the actual statuses again:
!issue-navigator-list-view.png!

Agile planning mode also uses the latter approach:
